### Backend — New Routes

#### [NEW] routes/authRoutes.js (upgraded)
- Fix JWT_SECRET (use env var, not hardcoded)
- Add `/api/auth/me` (get current user profile)
- Add `/api/auth/update-profile` (update health profile)

#### [NEW] routes/reportRoutes.js
- `POST /api/reports` — add new lab report
- `GET /api/reports` — get all reports for user (sorted by date)
- `GET /api/reports/:id` — get single report
- `DELETE /api/reports/:id` — delete report

#### [NEW] routes/aiRoutes.js (Groq-powered)
- `POST /api/ai/predict-risk` — send biomarkers → Groq LLM → returns `{ heartRisk, diabetesRisk, explanation, keyFactors[] }`
- `POST /api/ai/simulate-lifestyle` — send modified lifestyle params → Groq → returns new risk scores
- `POST /api/ai/doctor-summary` — send historical reports → Groq → returns paragraph summary
- `POST /api/ai/explainable-ai` — send biomarkers → Groq → returns ranked factor importance

#### [NEW] routes/alertRoutes.js
- `GET /api/alerts` — rule-based threshold alerts from latest report
  - glucose > 110 → ⚠️ High Glucose
  - LDL > 160 → 🔴 High LDL
  - BP > 140/90 → 🔴 Hypertension
  - HDL < 40 → ⚠️ Low HDL
  - etc.

#### [NEW] middleware/authMiddleware.js
- Verify JWT token from `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header

